OL,3,CTeletext on the web
OL,4,C
OL,5,GWebfaxFis produced using software that
OL,6,Femulates the 1970s teletext standard.
OL,8,FTeletext is widely regarded as being
OL,9,Fthe forerunner to the internet.
OL,11,FIt involved the use of spare capacity
OL,12,Fin the analogue TV signal to transmit
OL,13,Ftext and low-resolution graphics which
OL,14,Fcould be displayed as "pages" on
OL,15,Fsuitably equipped TV sets.
OL,17,FThe pioneers of teletext wereGCeefaxF
OL,18,F(BBC) andGORACLEF(IBA), launched in
OL,19,F1974 and 1978 respectively.
OL,21,FAt its peak in the mid-1990s teletext
OL,22,Fattracted 10m viewers a week in the UK.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,AInformationBWhat's New CRound-UpFNat TV
